    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but that's just being optimistic, isn't it? i'm not talking about a bad mood or a rough patch. i mean the actual core of who i am is just... shattered. like, you can't put a vase back together and expect it to hold water again. even if you glue it, it's still cracked. it's still fundamentally different. i just feel like there's no point in trying to 'move forward' when the foundation is gone.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
